channel.title: How do i log into moparscape v3.2 client?
channel.description:
I'm on level 1 so to speak and every time i try to log in it says "your account is already logged in"
Help!!!

item.title: How do i log into moparscape v3.2 client?
item.dc:creator: @Wintercanon Wintercanon
item.description:
@Wintercanon wrote:

You have to host a server on your own machine, or put in the hostname if it’s on another computer. The “your account is already logged in” response is usually an error to do with the server you’re trying to connect to. It’s a player updating problem that Winterlove derived servers have.
